{"tid":349424,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"硬件撚 討論硬件知識、砌機list、解答問題集中帖( 37）","createTime":"2017-08-06T14:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-09T02:15:10.000Z","uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b1cc92105dcfd896708d482e0ea61f35150119f0","tid":349424,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T14:16:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">新人求List需知</span></span></div></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為方面眾爸打可以好好幫助你<br />\n請你也需好好合作<br />\n不但可以盡快回復你的問題<br />\n更可以令條List更適合你所需<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 電腦主要用途 <br />\n純打機，定還需要直播和拍片等功能<br />\n<br />\n2. 目標<br />\n砌機為左玩咩GAME，玩咩類型(Steam有過千萬隻GAME，講清楚想邊一隻)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 個人需求<br />\n過求性價比?晝質效能(高，中，低，全開)?想未來幾年不用再更新電腦?超頻能力?<br />\n<br />\n4. 筆直<br />\n如果你筆直上限好寬鬆一定要講明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n5. 現在或將會便用MON的類型(1080P?2K?4K?144HZ?)<br />\n你既MON其實會限制硬件效能，哪怕再勁既電腦，但用不適合MON的話....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n6. 自己都學習一些<br />\n講真，有一班爸打們好撚憎伸手黨，只需做多一兩步<br />\n哪怕你直接照抄悠二巴打List放上黎問，佢地都會出手幫助<br />\n只是Ctrl C和Ctrl V咁簡單，大家都會開心既事點解唔做呢<br />\n甚至可能你在過程中已經搵到需要的答案都不一定!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n(悠二List網站 : <a href=\"http://yujihw.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyujihw.com%2F&d=uYwB4PLRKne2vcpGXkwSA5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=3f9f97c3\" target=\"_blank\">http://yujihw.com/</a>)<br />\n<br />\n7. 有信仰請出聲<br />\n廢事巴打們出完條LIST呢樣唔要嗰樣又唔要，當然你可能會浪費了一個更好的選擇<br />\n<br />\n8. 電腦硬件/IT領域中常見的用語對照表<br />\n(悠二List網站 : <a href=\"http://yujihw.com/edu/chinese\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyujihw.com%2Fedu%2Fchinese&d=uYwB4PLRKne2vcpGXkwSA5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=9b241e66\" target=\"_blank\">http://yujihw.com/edu/chinese</a>)"},{"pid":"9b48ecb7c4d022e6badd9dcc8d9beffac2bf30a8","tid":349424,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-06T14:17:08.000Z","msg":"1001唔開post可恥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c770052335f6a96daa4ce9f0851f135602d8e1e4","tid":349424,"uid":28450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-08T13:48:11.000Z","msg":"之前有位巴打出左post問好似唔錯<br />\n所以想問佢個list如何<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nAMD RYZEN R5 1600 3.2Ghz<br />\n<br />\nGigabyte GA-AB350M-Gaming 3<br />\n<br />\nGalax GeForce Gtx 1060 Oc 6GB GDDR5<br />\n<br />\nG.Skill DDR4 Aegis Gaming series 3000 MHz 2x8gb F4-3000c16D<br />\n<br />\nAntex Neoeco II Series NEO-ECO2-450 80Plus Bronze 450W<br />\n<br />\nWD Blue WD10EZEX 1TB 7200rpm<br />\n<br />\nKingston SSDNow UV400 240GB<br />\n<br />\nASYS 24x DVD<br />\n<br />\nAntex GX330 Window Gaminf ATX Case<br />\n<br />\n想問下咁樣砌如何？<br />\n同埋機箱依個係咪都ok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c54f1c7e22daf8cf779ebddc21c5451628a898c","tid":349424,"uid":34061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T01:56:00.000Z","msg":"I7 7700<br />\n8GB ram x 2<br />\n H110M Pro-VH<br />\n1060 3GB<br />\nSSD 240<br />\nHDD 1TB<br />\n連450W 牛 case<br />\n接近7000<br />\n<br />\n定買悠二巴打7000list<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/095039_d6cea610e62b86ab86c6dc6f75fd1d0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F095039_d6cea610e62b86ab86c6dc6f75fd1d0a.jpg&h=d32d0d73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n用黎打機Fps (overwatch) 同pc game <br />\n唔求全高效 普普通通就ok<br />\n同要推viewsonic 隻 xg2401 144Hz 1080moon<del></del><br />\n<br />\n另外想問下點解悠二條list用8GB ram 夠用？<br />\n<br />\n有勞巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d0cea4a624b76373d2db7d641ee17a23fd6ce75","tid":349424,"uid":78143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:03:31.000Z","msg":"硬件撚 討論硬件知識、砌機list、解答問題集中帖(37)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/349400/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/349400/page/1</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6c376fb82ed0d51eb15b4adee2452ba5b3161175","tid":349424,"uid":76523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-09T02:15:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/08/09/100638_c7f6903db5c0e98b7e01e54ec05a489c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F08%2F09%2F100638_c7f6903db5c0e98b7e01e54ec05a489c.jpg&h=6ca5668a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主要打機睇片，hd同碟機用舊所以張list無<br />\n<br />\n新手唔識，有無話咩配咩效能會好d，供電方面650w夠唔夠定係750w好啲<br />\n<br />\nCSGO/PUBG/黑色沙漠<br />\n<br />\n畫質中高左右<br />\n<br />\n大約預萬4萬5蚊<br />\n<br />\nmom係1080p <br />\n<br />\n無信仰，但想部機有燈得閒可以J下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n麻煩Ching<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}